Package: poodleR
Title: POOled donor Deconvolution by LEast square Regression
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Marta", "Perez-Alcantara", email = "martapalcantara@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Marta Perez-Alcantara <martapalcantara@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for estimating donor proportions in pooled sequencing
    experiments from genotype calls and per-variant read counts. The package
    provides helpers to convert VCF genotypes to allele dosages, derive allele
    frequencies from bam-readcount output, and solve the constrained regression
    problem used for pooled donor deconvolution.
